data.post_content:
Bridesmaids Gift Box Sets make the perfect proposal gift to pop the question "will you be my bridesmaid?" to the girls in your bridal party. Each complete set includes all the items listed below packaged together with white shred in a white round gift box. A mini “hello beautiful” card (blank inside) is included for you to hand write in on your own.

***Details***

This listing is for ONE Complete Gift Box with contents listed below and personalized with her name and short text under name on top of the box.

Box labeled with ★ REAL FOIL ★ choose METALLIC GOLD, SILVER OR ROSE GOLD - all items in gift box will match accordingly to your foil color choice.

***WHAT INCLUDED***

1 round gift box – lid labeled in the foil color, pattern, name, and short message of your choice
1 heart matchbox
1 candle tin – with rose pattern label
1 clear shatterproof flute with cheers
1 personalized compact mirror with a black polka dot design and name
1 polka dot lip balm
1 hello beautiful mini card (blank inside)
1 extra sticker – can be used or discarded – comes printed with the same name and same short text as the top of box – perfect for a mini bottle or another gift item you may add on your own - this extra sticker will be at the bottom of the box in case you choose not to use it.
